nodes.text: Jason Swank is a Marketing Executive and award winning Podcast host. Jason is one of the hosts of the award winning RebelForce Radio, a marketing exectutive for the Playhouse Square in Cleveland, and is a former host of The ForceCast. He and his RebelForce Radio co-host, Jimmy McInerney, were the Star Wars Celebration Anaheim Behind-The-Scenes Stage in 2015.
